GeoCode-Release
===============

This repository is the public distribution channel for GeoCode, a desktop
fork of OpenCode (https://github.com/sst/opencode) focused on GIS workflows.

We are grateful to the SST team and every OpenCode contributor for
building the foundation this project stands on. The original OpenCode
source remains MIT-licensed and Copyright (c) 2025 opencode; see
LICENSE for the full notice.
